data.title: Claudio Bieler
data.meta_description: Claudio Bieler. Self: Fox Sports: Copa Libertadores
data.text:
Forward for C.A. Colón (2005-06), Atlético de Rafaela (2006-07, 2020-), Colo-Colo (2007), L.D.U. Quito (2008-09, 2011-12), Racing Club de Avellaneda (2010), Newell's Old Boys (2011), Sporting Kansas City (2013-14), Quilmes A.C. (2015), C.A. Belgrano (2016-17), San Martín de Tucumán (2017-18) and C.S.D. Independiente del Valle (2019).

Honours with Colo-Colo: Chilean Primera División (2007 Clausura). Honours with L.D.U. Quito: Copa Libertadores (2008); Recopa Sudamericana (2009); Copa Sudamericana (2009). Honours with Sporting Kansas City: MLS Cup (2013). Honours with C.S.D. Independiente del Valle: Copa Sudamericana (2019).

Was named in the South America Team of the Year in 2009.
